168
00:08:11,430 --> 00:08:15,160
指控者将轰炸南部这里的一个斯库鲁要塞
The Accusers will bomb a Skrull stronghold here in the south.

169
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:18,250
我们潜入  找到索拉
We slip in, we locate Soh-Larr...

170
00:08:18,690 --> 00:08:21,450
