I can't believe you got in the raddest dogfight ever...

1341
01:46:32,280 --> 01:46:33,300
而我没看到
and I missed it.

1342
01:46:33,300 --> 01:46:35,150
要我说  你到的正是时候
I'd say you arrived just in time.

1343
01:46:35,150 --> 01:46:37,430
你飞得真的很漂亮
Some nifty flying you did out there.

1344
01:46:37,540 --> 01:46:39,750
神盾局总是需要你这样的好飞行员
S.H.I.E.L.D. could always use a good pilot like you.

1345
01:46:39,750 --> 01:46:41,260
我会考虑的
I'll consider it...

1346
01:46:41,800 --> 01:46:44,430
只要你不再说我的飞行"漂亮"
as long as you never call my flying "nifty" again.

1347
01:46:44,990 --> 01:46:46,150
你的眼睛怎么样了
How's your eye?

1348
01:46:46,990 --> 01:46:48,120
每秒都在愈合
Getting better every second.

1349
01:46:48,120 --> 01:46:49,570
我想问清楚
Just so I'm clear...

1350
01:46:49,910 --> 01:46:51,290
索拉
you were Soh-Larr...

1351
01:46:51,290 --> 01:46:53,790
-和那个神盾特工都是你  -凯勒
- and the S.H.I.E.L.D. agent? - Keller.

1352
01:46:53,900 --> 01:46:56,480
他把我上司绑了起来  盗用了他的身份
He tied my boss up, stole his identity.

1353
01:46:56,480 --> 01:46:59,490
我只是借了他的脸  我不是贼
I borrowed his likeness. I'm no thief.

1354
01:46:59,490 --> 01:47:00,980
是有点像盗窃
It is a little like stealing.

1355
01:47:01,130 --> 01:47:02,580
你是谁那边的
Whose side are you on here?

1356
01:47:02,580 --> 01:47:04,300
你康复前都可以在这里养伤
You're good to go here until you recover...

1357
01:47:04,300 --> 01:47:07,340
但你和你家人得换副新模样
but you and your family are gonna need a new look.

1358
01:47:07,340 --> 01:47:09,350
我可以继续做你上司
I could go back to being your boss.

1359
01:47:09,550 --> 01:47:10,240
千万别
Please don't.

1360
01:47:10,240 --> 01:47:13,300
怎么了  我喜欢他那双漂亮的蓝眼睛
Come on. I loved sporting his beautiful blue eyes.

1361
01:47:13,300 --> 01:47:15,740
说什么呢  你们的眼睛最漂亮了
No way. You guys have the best eyes.

1362
01:47:15,970 --> 01:47:18,020
-永远别变你的眼睛  -她的眼睛是很美
- Don't ever change your eyes. - She has beautiful eyes.

1363
01:47:18,030 --> 01:47:18,950
多谢你了
That's very sweet of you.

1364
01:47:18,950 --> 01:47:20,960
我想努力不慌乱
I was trying not to panic...

1365
01:47:21,340 --> 01:47:22,850
我会帮你们找到家的
I'll help you find a home.

1366
01:47:23,860 --> 01:47:25,610
完成玛威尔的心愿
Finish what Mar-Vell started.

1367
01:47:27,100 --> 01:47:29,300
他们可以跟我们住这儿
They can stay here with us.

1368
01:47:29,300 --> 01:47:30,460
不是吗  妈妈
Can't they, Mom?

1369
01:47:31,090 --> 01:47:32,900
他们在这里不安全的  宝贝
They won't be safe here, baby.

1370
01:47:33,670 --> 01:47:35,080
卡罗尔阿姨是对的
Auntie Carol's right.

1371
01:47:35,630 --> 01:47:36,920
他们得有自己的家
They need their own home.

1372
01:47:37,640 --> 01:47:39,410
我很快就会回来
I'll be back before you know it.

1373
01:47:40,350 --> 01:47:43,010
或许我可以飞上天  跟你碰头
Or maybe I could fly up and meet you halfway?

1374
01:47:43,020 --> 01:47:45,830
那你得学会像卡罗尔阿姨那样发光
Only if you learn to glow like your Auntie Carol.

1375
01:47:45,830 --> 01:47:47,680
或许我可以建艘飞船
Or maybe I'll build a spaceship.

1376
01:47:47,680 --> 01:47:49,760
-你又说不准  -是啊
- You don't know. - He doesn't.

1377
01:47:59,190 --> 01:48:01,490
把宇宙魔方留在地球上
Keep the Tesseract on Earth.

1378
01:48:02,290 --> 01:48:03,240
藏好
Hidden.

1379
01:48:03,420 --> 01:48:05,490
你确定那是马威会想要的吗
You sure that's what Marvel would want?

1380
01:48:06,190 --> 01:48:07,440
是玛威尔
Mar-Vell.

1381
01:48:07,470 --> 01:48:08,810
我就那么说的
That's what I said.

1382
01:48:08,860 --> 01:48:11,440
是两个词  玛  威尔
It's two words. Mar. Vell.

1383
01:48:11,440 --> 01:48:12,760
玛威尔
Mar-Vell.

1384
01:48:12,760 --> 01:48:13,990
"马威"听上去好多了
"Marvel" sounds a lot better.

1385
01:48:13,990 --> 01:48:15,700
就像惊艳合唱团
You know, like the Marvelettes.

1386
01:48:29,330 --> 01:48:30,550
没印象吗
Not ringing any bells?

1387
01:48:30,550 --> 01:48:32,450
继续唱  或许我会想起来
Keep singing. Maybe it'll come back to me.

1388
01:48:47,780 --> 01:48:49,250
我给它升级了
I upgraded it.

1389
01:48:49,890 --> 01:48:52,750
信号范围能至少覆盖几个星系了
Range should be a couple galaxies, at least.

1390
01:48:55,180 --> 01:48:57,450
怎么  你觉得我会给你打骚扰电话吗
What? You think I'm gonna crank call you?

1391
01:48:57,450 --> 01:49:00,620
仅限紧急情况
For emergencies only, okay?

1392
01:49:07,030 --> 01:49:08,080
好吧
Well...

1393
01:49:08,320 --> 01:49:10,780
如果你再路过这个星系
if you're ever passing back through this galaxy...

1394
01:49:10,850 --> 01:49:12,580
务必喊我一声
be sure to give a brother a shout.

1395
01:49:29,580 --> 01:49:31,360
我们洗干净了番茄酱的污迹
We got the ketchup stain off.

1396
01:49:37,000 --> 01:49:38,660
谢谢  捣蛋中尉
Thanks, Lieutenant Trouble.

1397
01:49:48,170 --> 01:49:50,010
我也不愿意道别
It's hard for me to say goodbye, too.

1398
01:50:04,380 --> 01:50:05,440
去吧
Go on.

1399
01:51:12,690 --> 01:51:14,080
很高兴你回来了  长官
Glad to have you back, sir.

1400
01:51:14,570 --> 01:51:15,670
这是寄给您的
This came for you.

1401
01:51:20,250 --> 01:51:21,470
是真的吗
So, is it true?

1402
01:51:22,420 --> 01:51:23,890
克里人烧毁了你的眼睛
That the Kree burned your eye out...

1403
01:51:23,890 --> 01:51:26,170
因为你不肯交出宇宙魔方
because you refused to give them the Tesseract?

1404
01:51:27,270 --> 01:51:31,320
我既不能承认也不能否认这种说法
I will neither confirm nor deny the facts of that story.

1405
01:51:31,320 --> 01:51:32,400
明白
Understood.

1406
01:51:33,910 --> 01:51:34,650
很遗憾
I'm sorry to report

1407
01:51:34,660 --> 01:51:36,210
我们仍尚未找到宇宙魔方
that we still haven't found the Tesseract.

1408
01:51:36,210 --> 01:51:38,150
它肯定会出现的
I'm sure it'll turn up somewhere.

1409
01:51:40,020 --> 01:51:41,460
等出现了我会通知您的
I'll let you know when it does.

1410
01:51:41,810 --> 01:51:42,900
然后呢
Then what?

1411
01:51:44,060 --> 01:51:45,040
长官
Sir?

1412
01:51:45,150 --> 01:51:49,270
我们完全不知道还存在怎样的跨星系威胁
We have no idea what other intergalactic threats are out there.

1413
01:51:49,370 --> 01:51:51,460
而我们的单人女子保安
And our one-woman security force

1414
01:51:51,470 --> 01:51:54,810
还要优先处理宇宙另一边的问题
had a prior commitment on the other side of the universe.

1415
01:51:57,660 --> 01:51:59,790
单靠神盾局不足以保护我们
S.H.I.E.L.D. alone can't protect us.

1416
01:52:01,460 --> 01:52:02,930
我们需要找到更多的
We need to find more.

1417
01:52:03,440 --> 01:52:04,430
更多武器吗
More weapons?

1418
01:52:04,440 --> 01:52:06,170
更多英雄
More heroes.

1419
01:52:06,170 --> 01:52:08,060
你觉得还能找到其他她这样的人
You think you can find others like her?

1420
01:52:08,070 --> 01:52:10,370
我们找到了她  而且还是没在找的时候
We found her, and we weren't even looking.

1421
01:52:12,010 --> 01:52:13,250
休息一下吧  长官
Get some rest, sir.

1422
01:52:14,350 --> 01:52:16,120
你要做个重要决定呢
You got a big decision to make.

1423
01:55:15,350 --> 01:55:16,830
这真是场噩梦
This is a nightmare.

1424
01:55:18,780 --> 01:55:20,680
我做的噩梦都比这强
I've had better nightmares.

1425
01:55:25,270 --> 01:55:27,580
那玩意停了
So, that thing just stopped doing

1426
01:55:27,580 --> 01:55:29,340
虽然也不知它在干什么
whatever the hell it was doing.

1427
01:55:31,090 --> 01:55:32,170
什么情况
What do we got?

1428
01:55:33,880 --> 01:55:36,380
它在发送的信号终于停止了
Whatever signal it was sending finally crapped out.

1429
01:55:36,380 --> 01:55:37,850
我们不是外接了电池吗
I thought we bypassed the battery.

1430
01:55:37,850 --> 01:55:38,680
是的
We did.

1431
01:55:38,680 --> 01:55:41,700
电还插着呢  它就是停了
It's still plugged in. It just stopped.

1432
01:55:42,450 --> 01:55:43,870
重启  再发一次信号
Reboot it. Send the signal again.

1433
01:55:43,870 --> 01:55:45,870
我们都不知道这是什么
We don't even know what this is.

1434
01:55:45,870 --> 01:55:48,190
弗瑞知道  照做吧
Fury did. Just do it, please.

1435
01:55:48,490 --> 01:55:50,600
一有信号就告诉我
You tell me the second you get a signal.

1436
01:55:51,290 --> 01:55:53,480
我想知道接收信号的人是谁
I wanna know who's on the other end of that thing.

1437
01:55:56,530 --> 01:55:57,930
弗瑞人呢
Where's Fury?

